# IntelPolitics - Political Accountability Platform

> Political transparency and accountability intelligence platform with politician dossiers, truthfulness tracking, and comparison tools. Lithuanian language (lt).

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 |
| Language | TypeScript |
| Headlines Font | Space Grotesk |
| Body Font | Inter |
| Design | "The Digital Panopticon" — technical brutalism, detective board logic |
| Language | Lithuanian (lt) with proper diacritics |

